{"type": "article", "id": 62967, "title": "紫砂壶太老套？它也可以做得年轻有趣｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-04-15T22:49:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 57915, "name": "Design Magnet"}, {"id": 57916, "name": "Joseph C. Furniture"}, {"id": 57917, "name": "Superpoly"}, {"id": 57918, "name": "Chiyonokame"}, {"id": 57919, "name": "TELLS STUDIO"}, {"id": 57920, "name": "Tangmode"}, {"id": 57921, "name": "Joseph Chun"}, {"id": 23191, "name": "Yuta Takahashi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 111, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190415211504iVyf3Wj5sHzuRlaS.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #101010} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #101010} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s8 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s9 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s10 {font: 11.0px 'Apple SD Gothic Neo'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Tangmode by TELLS STUDIO</h3><p>堂前百货（Tangmode）是由挑时工作室全权负责产品设计的新品牌，以宜兴紫砂为设计媒介，全面拓展紫砂材质的边界，带来更多属于年轻人的紫砂器皿。堂前百货，是一个来自中国的全新生活器皿品牌。</p><p>贝雷壶茶壶摆脱传统茶具的造型束缚，赋予现代设计的趣味重塑。迷宫茶漏壶，像是消失在历史文明的古老国度，倒置于水中的奇幻城堡。戴利娅花瓶的灵感源自雅典卫城的古老遗迹，浑然天成的优雅极致。初枝花瓶的玻璃直筒可以向上延展和替换，让花瓶也可以随着植物一同生长。束瓶冷水瓶拥有不同材质的球形瓶盖。勺味调味瓶，创造与日常截然不同的倾倒角度，平行的器皿与垂直的液体，秩序感带来更多的仪式感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904152115506mCiq5eRZGPF8HVN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211550NsuF2c8V7dWXBQ0G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211550gBVMU14W8ZmAraqd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211550xlCSuKjyHgQvI5cG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904152115511Hf65PTJ0rGlc9IW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211551NqCLM3hVuBAyxi2K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211551kocwYh2z5uDgf73s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211551No937MGhCdgYAw4R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904152115527RLB9GF3agJ8PUQn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211552ASwvktZ6CBnG1Dmu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211552jmPNpc6B70reOwoS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211552jeabu3GOAJcfUDKZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211552IakHBYXKbpteu6Qr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211553W5oFpcST4MkRfyOX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Chiyonokame by Yuta Takahashi </h3><p>Chiyonokame 是在日本拥有 300 多年历史的一家酿酒厂。最近，他们委托日本艺术总监和设计师 Yuta Takahashi，为其季节性的清酒产品 Hime Nigori 和 Hime Hanabi 重新设计了包装。</p><p>Yuta Takahashi 称其灵感来自米粒和稻田，白色标签让人想起米粒，他创造了一个简单的排版，大面积的留白很百搭，比如粉红色的玻璃代表盛开的樱花，蓝色玻璃代表天空和海洋，磨砂的玻璃瓶唤起了日本清酒的概念。设计师试图借力这些元素的组合，表达出对日本清酒文化丰富历史的尊重和恰当的敬意。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211639PtszA35HVf2hNC71.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211639JzVXMtafmKOIZSHB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211639nuraESD82MPk60Lg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211640gW0jfqphvcmEx9LB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211640cEa4MRYpn2rTLXDU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211641I6JqimQcYOht9eL2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211641orSdVxQDMZng589w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904152116399Ob4JXFBk8thMSrI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yutatakahashi.jp/work/chiyonokame/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yuta Takahashi</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Postcard Collection by Superpoly</h3><p>在今年的 Nomad 设计展上，法国设计工作室 Superpoly 为哥本哈根画廊 Etage Projects 量身定制了明信片系列的家具和家居用品。</p><p>Postcard 系列新品包括橱柜、椅子、边桌、落地灯和两盏台灯。据 Superpoly 的两位创始人 Antoine Grulier 和 Thomas Defour 透露，这个系列的灵感来自他们在海边消夏的回忆。Postcard 系列拥有鲜艳的色彩和简约的手工制作形式。</p><p>另一个灵感来源是在法国南部沿海建造的现代战后度假屋，比如爱尔兰建筑师 Eileen Grey 1929 年建造的 E-1027 别墅。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211731sCr3YO40zIxJ15kN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562183\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211731rqj8no2DEVxeskRd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.846024\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211731teIR6K4EroONuVT1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211732WcyOHdA6RGe4ju5X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211733YtLrAbWfG5XvRgsP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211732WTCHqYIoV0nG5Lc3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.etageprojects.com/superpoly-1\" rel=\"nofollow\">Etage Projects</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Joseph Chun’s Furniture</h3><p>崭露头角的布鲁克林家具设计师 Joseph Chun 创立了个人品牌 Joseph C. Furniture，主打手工制作的木制品。</p><p>在成长过程中，他遇见并经历了几种不同的文化，从首尔到威斯康辛州，从北卡罗来纳到朝鲜军队，现在他从这些记忆中汲取灵感，试图用作品来分享他的故事。</p><p>目前出品的这六件作品包括 C 书桌、Zieut 椅子、Curved 长凳、Personal 桌子、Léa 咖啡桌，以及 Motivation Pack 柜子。</p><p>比如 Motivation Pack 柜子的灵感，源自他在军队中的灵感，一个专门用来收纳普通士兵日常必需品的柜子。又如 Léa 咖啡桌，以其第一个侄女 Léa 的名字命名，无边角设计，即使幼儿居住的空间也可以安全使用。Zieut 椅子的灵感来自于韩语字母 ㅈ 等等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904152118383DaZiJhVugGR5bB1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665432\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211838ryS9sjRI017Y5oCX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665432\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211838l2i74KJuQtfR9nhz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211838bqoYlCJ7UxMkEFcN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211839g3TycMhxtAUlIVjs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211839Q9KZNMGpY10nkyRc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211839rGH1I627kWR9X3zw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665432\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211840srwhOo65TPctdlLu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904152118416rElNM921Cznb7kv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211841jpOCTKnUEHwhdkAu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502469\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://josephcfurniture.com/work\" rel=\"nofollow\">Joseph C. Furniture</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Balance Watch by Design Magnet</h3><p>顾名思义，这款名为 Balance 的手表的名字，精准诠释了它的表盘设计。据称，Design Magnet</p><p> 团队的灵感取自阴阳，黑白两色将表盘分为两个截然不同的部分，同时也在暗喻这款手表的双重性，不只是颜色，这也是一款半数字形态的手表。</p><p>它看起来像普通的机械表，但表盘实际上是动态电子墨水显示器的一半部件。此外，电子墨水显示屏还有一个“子表盘”，用于显示日期和时间。电子墨水显示屏甚至可以在连接时与用户的手机配合使用，在用户接到电话或消息时提供通知。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904152119261wxVgyb3f6iLC8TZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211926BOZPvuinzxQ72XTR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211927QinyUTw7soJpXLPf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211927mzijO9veTShyPaGr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211927Fj0Y3zcwOphQRedB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211927JezWk7MdqVSXvNba.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211927t1wVHAnFrUGsydx7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211928qc2dBvIw3UJnuzpL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211928hgR6C5OidlD1y2WY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190415211928hLG0AX2KkzwIY9qW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.yankodesign.com/2019/04/12/the-balance-watch-bases-itself-off-the-duality-of-yin-and-yang/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}